\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'93Old man, what you say is very true.\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0470\uc0\u8232 But come now, tell me\'97and tell me truly\'97\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0[380]\u8232 are you sending so much treasure out\u8232 for foreign people to keep safe for you,\u8232 or are you leaving sacred Ilion\u8232 in fear, now that the finest man\'92s been killed,\u8232 your own son, who never was reluctant\u8232 in any battles with Achaeans.\'94\
